                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Avenir' fontsize='10'>• Customers aged 18–24 exhibit the highest churn rates.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Avenir' fontsize='10'>• New customers are twice as likely to leave as long-tenured customers.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Avenir' fontsize='10'>• Low-engagement customers are 6x more likely to churn.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
